## Importance of AI in Recruitment

AI can help organizations:

- Reduce manual screening time
- Improve hiring efficiency
- Support objective decision-making
- Handle large candidate datasets effectively

However, it is important to ensure **ethical and unbiased AI systems in recruitment**.

